messages.message:
API request used to render the consumption chart is `/automation-metrics/`  (automation_metrics.py)
Sample payload:
```{
    "deployment_id": "0196a311-236f-731d-afae-272b5a299a93",
    "start_time": 1746828000000,
    "end_time": 1747432800000,
    "aggregations": [
        {
            "name": "deployment_metrics",
            "type": "CUSTOM-METRIC",
            "options": {
                "metric_name": "DEPLOYMENT-LEVEL-ACCUMULATE"
            }
        }
    ]
}```
